{"title":"神父客串模特（附图片）","authors":["朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"神父客串模特"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗  朱根华  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载，英国南部不久前举办了一场别开生面的时装表演，一些专职神父穿着各种法衣、圣带，昂首挺胸登场亮相。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管神职在身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟还是凡人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活在花花世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以看破红尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目睹名模献艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾倒芸芸众生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神父大受启发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要披挂上阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身着法衣圣带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加入模特大军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个仪态万方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风姿不让红粉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也算履行神职，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无损教士身份。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿上帝保佑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿门！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}